(c_0,\|.\|)
\{x^k\}, \{y^k\}\subset c_0
\|x^k\|=\|y^k\|=1
\|x^k-y^k\|\geq \frac{1}{2}
 x^k_i= \begin{cases} \frac{1}{2}\sqrt{1-\frac{1}{(k+1)^2}-\frac{1}{(k+2)^2}}& \text{if}\quad i=1\\ \frac{1}{2}& \text{if}\quad i\in\{k+1, k+2\} \\ 0&\text{if}\quad\text{otherwise} \end{cases}  
 y^k_i= \begin{cases} \frac{1}{2}\sqrt{1-\frac{1}{k^2}-\frac{1}{(k+2)^2}}& \text{if}\quad i=1\\ \frac{1}{2}& \text{if}\quad i\in\{k, k+2\} \\ 0&\text{if}\quad\text{otherwise} \end{cases}  
 \left\|\frac{x^k+y^k}{2}\right\|\longrightarrow 1 \quad\text{as}\quad k\longrightarrow \infty. 
